Christine Elise https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christine_Elise 0 Christine Elise (born February 12, 1965) is an American film and television actress. She is best known for her roles as Emily Valentine in Beverly Hills, 90210 and Kyle in Child's Play 2 (1990), and Cult of Chucky (2017, Cameo, Unrated Version Only).
